<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bag" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bag,</orth> sack, pouch: <cit><quote>a b. of flax,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 159</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>put your pipes in your b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 1, 20</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>balmed and entreasured with full --s of spices,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 66</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a b. of money,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.177" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 177</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sums in sealed --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 16</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the b. of gold,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 4, 99</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.8.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 8, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 178</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.131" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.280" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 280</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 41</bibl>. <cit><quote>With b. and baggage:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 170</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.206" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 206</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>